Following are the steps to be followed to setup Spark and Scala Locally

Step:1 
Download spark from http://spark.apache.org/downloads.html 

Step:2
Download http://www.scala-lang.org/download

Step:3
Extract scala and Add scala home directory to PATH variable
export SCALA_HOME=/Users/ondrej/scala-2.10.4 
export PATH=$PATH:$SCALA_HOME/bin

Step:4
Extract spark and navigate to spark home directoy, run following command
sbt/sbt clean assembly

Step:5
Navigate to spark home directory and start spark shell
./bin/spark-shell
